{"tid":968351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"這羊沒有非洲豬瘟慘遭性侵　男辯「牠自願的」","createTime":"2019-01-04T07:25:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T11:43:23.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7ccef394699b66197ff16f63b22c28c1d3a0c03e","tid":968351,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T07:25:28.000Z","msg":"非洲國家馬拉威有一隻羊，牠沒有落入非洲豬瘟的厄運裡，卻慘遭一名21歲男子坎巴尼(Kennedy Kambani)性侵，坎巴尼更辯稱「牠自願的」。<br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，這頭羊原本是當地農家馬胡利卡(Pemphero Mwakhulika)所飼養的羊隻。但在近日，馬胡利卡發現這頭羊不見了，並強烈懷疑被坎巴尼偷走，於是告知附近鄉民，並通報警方。待鄉民們找到羊羊的時候，卻看到驚人的一幕，坎巴尼正在性侵羊兒。之後坎巴尼被警方逮捕，控以虐待動物罪，坎巴尼雖然承認與羊羊性交，但他堅稱有獲得這頭羊「咩~~咩~~」同意，於是進行人獸交。<br />\n全案已進入司法程序偵辦中，但當局仍然不公布受害羊的性別。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aLZJ8KL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaLZJ8KL.png&h=a5bc817b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3uzx14M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3uzx14M.png&h=94a767f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31b11ae1ff34f3b3dbe2530cb0d71502fd6cceb6","tid":968351,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T07:37:45.000Z","msg":"冇繡球<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d583dd19c4dae420d27e53f070c3eb679f5d152","tid":968351,"uid":121773,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T07:40:11.000Z","msg":"但當局仍然不公布受害羊的性別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d79f29d1266ed7ba9bfe28560dbf44d7d54915fb","tid":968351,"uid":195169,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T07:40:15.000Z","msg":"非洲國家馬拉威有一隻羊，牠沒有落入非洲豬瘟的厄運裡<br />\n<br />\n乜撚野, 爛GAG? <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cb8027c4daf5df99c14a3d055674f775d917633","tid":968351,"uid":34757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T07:41:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e480d238c7064ff80ad2521af4e5f5b3c4ac25d7","tid"